## {{#if (eq project.language "pt-BR")}}Protocolo de Execucao{{else}}Execution Protocol{{/if}}

{{#if (eq project.language "pt-BR")}}
1. **ANALISAR** — Identificar tipo de artefato, verificar skills e regras aplicaveis
2. **DECIDIR** — Skill existe? → invocar. Sem skill + repetitivo? → criar skill. Trivial? → implementar
3. **EXECUTAR** — Seguir output da skill OU aplicar regras diretamente
4. **VALIDAR** — Executar cadeia de validacao obrigatoria (lint → test → build)
{{else}}
1. **ANALYZE** — Identify artifact type, check applicable skills and rules
2. **DECIDE** — Skill exists? → invoke. No skill + repetitive? → create skill. Trivial? → implement
3. **EXECUTE** — Follow skill output OR apply rules directly
4. **VALIDATE** — Run mandatory validation chain (lint → test → build)
{{/if}}

