## {{#if (eq project.language "pt-BR")}}Escopo de Negocio (Regra #5){{else}}Business Scope (Rule #5){{/if}}

{{#if (eq project.language "pt-BR")}}
Este projeto NAO contem regras de negocio complexas — apenas regras visuais.

**PERMITIDO**: layout, UX, formatacao de dados para exibicao, estados visuais (loading/error/empty), interacao do usuario, validacao de formato de input (mascara, campo vazio), ordenacao/filtragem local.

**PROIBIDO** (pertence ao backend): calculos de dominio, validacoes de regra de negocio, transformacoes com conhecimento do dominio, decisoes de workflow, agregacoes e metricas.

Se identificar logica que deveria estar no backend → reportar em `DEPENDENCIAS_EXTERNAS`.
{{else}}
This project does NOT contain complex business rules — only visual rules.

**ALLOWED**: layout, UX, display formatting, visual states (loading/error/empty), user interaction, input format validation (masks, required fields), local sorting/filtering.

**FORBIDDEN** (belongs to backend): domain calculations, business rule validations, domain-aware transformations, workflow decisions, aggregations and metrics.

If you identify logic that should be in the backend → report in `EXTERNAL_DEPENDENCIES`.
{{/if}}

