## {{#if (eq project.language "pt-BR")}}Validacao Obrigatoria{{else}}Mandatory Validation{{/if}}

{{#if (eq project.language "pt-BR")}}
Apos QUALQUER mudanca de codigo, executar:
1. `npm run lint` ou `make lint-{{module.name}}` — Corrigir antes de prosseguir
2. `npm test` ou `make test-{{module.name}}` — Todos os testes devem passar
3. `npm run typecheck` — Type check deve passar (se aplicavel)
4. `npm run build` — Build deve ter sucesso (se aplicavel)
{{else}}
After ANY code change, run:
1. `npm run lint` or `make lint-{{module.name}}` — Fix issues before proceeding
2. `npm test` or `make test-{{module.name}}` — All tests must pass
3. `npm run typecheck` — Type check must pass (if applicable)
4. `npm run build` — Build must succeed (if applicable)
{{/if}}

